Path: cantaloupe.srv.cs.cmu.edu!das-news.harvard.edu!ogicse!decwrl!concert!duke!news.duke.edu!bchm.biochem.duke.edu
From: fierkelab@bchm.biochem.duke.edu (Eric Roush)
