References: <mssC50DFw.71u@netcom.com> <1993Apr5.151834.14257@cs.cornell.edu> <mssC50qA5.Dtv@netcom.com> <7975@blue.cis.pitt.edu>
Date: Tue, 6 Apr 1993 16:54:23 GMT
Nntp-Posting-Host-[nntpd-681]: sn01.sncc.lsu.edu
