From: mse@cc.bellcore.com (25836-michael evenchick(F113))
Subject: Re: DAVE KINGMAN FOR THE HALL OF FAME
Organization: Bellcore, Livingston, NJ
Date: Thu, 15 Apr 93 21:44:25 GMT
Message-ID: <1993Apr15.214425.17005@porthos.cc.bellcore.com>
Followup-To: Re: DAVE KINGMAN FOR THE HALL OF FAME
