Message-ID: <13591@news.duke.edu>
Date: 20 Apr 93 15:52:02 GMT
References: <1993Apr17.132559.1@ulkyvx.louisville.edu> <13512@news.duke.edu> <1993Apr19.194025.8967@adobe.com>
